{"type":null,"faqId":32880,"title":"【EMUI3.1及以上】音乐-锁屏歌词&桌面歌词","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>相信很多花粉都遇到过这种情况：听歌的时候想看到歌词又不想停留在音乐模块，想一边使用其他app一边看歌词，或者直接在锁屏界面看歌词，不用每次都进入音乐播放器界面。这时可采用华为音乐【锁屏&amp;桌面歌词】功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤：打开音乐播放器，进入设置，打开桌面歌词开关。播放一首歌曲后，即可在桌面／锁屏看到歌词。你还可以调整桌面歌词的字体大小和颜色。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=102318\" style=\"width:2.7118056in;height:4.820833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7600","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748436000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":7,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"音乐,锁屏歌词,桌面歌词","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}